    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <ref refid="structboost_1_1geometry_1_1closeable__view" kindref="compound">closeable_view</ref> is used internally by the library to handle all rings, either closed or open, the same way. The default method is closed, all algorithms process rings as if they are closed. Therefore, if they are opened, a view is created which closes them. The <ref refid="structboost_1_1geometry_1_1closeable__view" kindref="compound">closeable_view</ref> might be used by library users, but its main purpose is internally. <parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
