<para>Original range </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Close</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Specifies if it the range is closed, if so, nothing will happen. If it is open, it will iterate the first point after the last point. </para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>    </detaileddescription>
